{"id": "1526186806670917693", "channel_id": "1526186806670917693", "author_id": "310562007978082304", "author_name": "miguelo6", "content": "Xu's Soulforge does not deal as much Fixed DMG as stated in its description when Spellbound is removed from a Humanoid enemy.\n\nAccording to her Soulforge's description, when removing Spellbound stacks from an enemy, 'each stack deals Fixed DMG equal to 9% of target's Max HP on \"Humanoid\" enemies.' This is not the case.\n\nI've attached some screenshots of a test I did against some Humanoid enemies in Wave 2 of the current D-Tide rotation. The test consisted of applying 5 Spellbound stacks on the enemies and then exalting on Xu, picking Enthrall.\n\nIn the attached screenshots, the Tailor, with a Max HP of 76,096, received 10,289 damage after Xu's exalt, with 277 Poison stacks applied. The enemy only took 13.5% of its Max HP as damage, with some of it originating from the Poison triggered by Xu's exalt.\n\nThe expected amount of damage was at least 45% or 50% of the enemy's Max HP, depending on whether the Fixed DMG dealt by Xu's exalt based on the number of Spellbound stacks present on an enemy, regardless of whether it's Humanoid or not, is additive with the damage alluded to by her Soulforge's description.", "timestamp": "2026-07-13T11:21:29.890000+00:00", "thread_id": "1526186806670917693", "attachments": [{"id": "1526186806884958258", "filename": "Screenshot_20260713_074005_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 346599, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1526186806670917693/1526186806884958258/Screenshot_20260713_074005_Morimens.jpg?ex=6a56c479&is=6a5572f9&hm=7474289308f8a14c56ec213485eae440a9128eba237bea3ab8b11551fb020882&"}, {"id": "1526186807325233322", "filename": "Screenshot_20260713_073947_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 338009, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1526186806670917693/1526186807325233322/Screenshot_20260713_073947_Morimens.jpg?ex=6a56c47a&is=6a5572fa&hm=92515d8477e5cdd62dfc554efa8e1a10ef2f326774ccfe4b113c44312f3127cd&"}, {"id": "1526186807765766235", "filename": "Screenshot_20260713_073841_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 335022, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1526186806670917693/1526186807765766235/Screenshot_20260713_073841_Morimens.jpg?ex=6a56c47a&is=6a5572fa&hm=3c7e99f7e20ee9e7035477ffa902923e9c14458c7529537cd851f7cb402cb4cb&"}, {"id": "1526186808214290574", "filename": "Screenshot_20260713_074617_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 274524, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1526186806670917693/1526186808214290574/Screenshot_20260713_074617_Morimens.jpg?ex=6a56c47a&is=6a5572fa&hm=479c0c2968e9fbd85dc9cb06e8e8981ad235b1cccaf79c05b117e6b0047188fd&"}]}
